document_data.name: Warehouse District of Skuld
document_data.mainbody: The '''Warehouse District''' was a walled section of the capital city of [[Skuld]] in [[Mulhorand]] during the midâ€“14{{th}} century [[DR]].{{Cite interactive atlas|490 Skuld}}
document_data.Location: The Warehouse District was located in the southwest part of Skuld along the north bank of the [[River of Shadows]].
document_data.Description: The entire district was walled. Two gateways were found in the northwest corner of the Warehouse District, allowing access to the [[Skuld/Central Ward|Central Ward]] to the north, and the [[Skuld/Merchant District|Merchant District]] to the west.
